
Boringtown Main Menu
====================
<B>     Bulletins
<C>     Comments to sysop
<E>     Read and Write private messages
<F>     File-menu
<G>     Log out
<L>     List Users
<M>     Messages menu
<O>     Page operator
<P>     Change Password
<V>     View version number


               Boringtown BBSs Filemeny
               ========================
<L> List files                  <ADD> Add file to HOLD
<D> Download a file             <DIR> List files in HOLD
<U> Upload a file               <EXT> Extract LZh-files to HOLD
<V> View a LZH file             <DEL> Remove files from HOLD
<Q> Back to main menu           <GET> Fetch files in HOLD
<S> Short filelist


Boringtown BBSs Bulletinmenu:
=============================
0. News
1. Information about the program
2. etc

<Q> Back to mainmenu
[Scrolling is stopped with CTRL-S and restored with Ctrl-Q]

Boringtown BBSs Sysopmenu
=========================
<B>ackup
<R>ead private messages
<L>ist user log
<D>elete user log         (local,Sysop)
<C>omments delete         (local,Sysop)
<Q>uit to main menu
<S>tart another script    (NO WAY BACK)

Or write the CLI-command you want to execute.

Boringtown BBSs Private Mail
=================================
<Q>  Back to Main menu
<R>  Read letters for you
<W>  Write a letter to someone
<E>  Erase all letters foro you
<G>  Grab all messages and letters in a file

Boringtowns BBSs Areamenu:
==========================
1. Common
2. Ideas

<R> Read messages
<W> Write messages

<Q> Back to Main menu
[Scrolling is stopped with Ctrl-S and resumed with Ctrl-Q]
